14
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,400
After I grew up,

15
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:13,840
and finished my study,

16
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,720
I vowed

17
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:18,200
